{"tha-ap153:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap153:0.2":"Bandhujivakavagga ","tha-ap153:0.3":"Bandhujivakattheraapadana ","tha-ap153:1.1":"“Candamva vimalam suddham, ","tha-ap153:1.2":"vippasannamanavilam; ","tha-ap153:1.3":"Nandibhavaparikkhinam, ","tha-ap153:1.4":"tinnam loke visattikam. ","tha-ap153:2.1":"Nibbapayantam janatam, ","tha-ap153:2.2":"Tinnam tarayatam varam; ","tha-ap153:2.3":"Munim vanamhi jhayantam, ","tha-ap153:2.4":"Ekaggam susamahitam. ","tha-ap153:3.1":"Bandhujivakapupphani, ","tha-ap153:3.2":"lagetva suttakenaham; ","tha-ap153:3.3":"Buddhassa abhiropayim, ","tha-ap153:3.4":"sikhino lokabandhuno. ","tha-ap153:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap153:4.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap153:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap153:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap153:5.1":"Ito sattamake kappe, ","tha-ap153:5.2":"manujindo mahayaso; ","tha-ap153:5.3":"Samantacakkhu namasi, ","tha-ap153:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap153:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap153:6.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap153:6.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap153:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap153:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma bandhujivako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap153:8.1":"Bandhujivakattherassapadanam pathamam. "}